Description:
On a rock you see a strange frog holding a broken instrument and looking sad. He suddenly jumps up and lands in your face:

"What's up guys... I'm Gustav, the globetrotting minstrel. I had a gig here in the swamp, but some crocomen tricked me into gambling and broke my lute.

What am I gonna do now without my lute? I can't just play with any instrument, it's gotta be stylish. The only lute similar to mine that I remember is in the elven mansion where I played some time ago, in Faeborg...
DescriptionAction: Think you could get it for me? I will pay for it."
